We apply your overtime rules in the following order: 

1. Entire Day Rules (i.e. Saturday = OT)
2. Daily Double (i.e. After 10 Hrs = Dbl)
3. Daily OT (i.e. After 8 Hrs = OT)
4. Nightly Rules (i.e. Between 6pm and 6am is OT)
5. Weekly OT Rules (i.e. After 40 Hrs = OT)

Note the following:
- Once time has been moved to OT, it is never moved back to Straight time
- Once time has been moved to Double, it is never moved back to OT or Straight time
